Template version: 1.0

This file marks the pristine, un-instantiated project template.
scripts/init-project.ps1 instantiates new projects only from a source that
carries this marker, reads the version above and writes it into the new
project's concept paper, then removes the marker from the instance. Bump
the version line when the template gains a notable change so instantiated
projects can be diffed against it later. Do not delete it from the
template; do not add it to an instantiated project.
